Stem change - Diphtongue:
Applies to indicative present and subjunctive present for 1st, 2nd, 3rd person singular and 3rd person plural (all except nosotros and vosotros)
o -> ue
acostarse
almorzar
contar
dormir
mover
poder
recordarse
soler
soñar
volver

e -> ie
cerrar
commenzar
despertarse
encender
merendar
pensar
querer
sentarse
sentir

u -> ue
jugar

Estar
estar is never followed by a noun
